This paper is about a recommendation system that incorporates multiple relations between items. It involves modeling user preferences based on different types of relations and their values. This work is relevant to several sub-categories of computer science, including information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), social and information networks (cs.SI), and databases (cs.DB).
